EmailTemplate.name: Pre-Purchase Review Form Reminder
EmailTemplate.subject: Pre-Purchase Review Form Reminder - {!Opportunity.Name}
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
{!Opportunity.OwnerFullName},
Thank you for making us aware of this opportunity. The next step is to complete a Commercial Pre-Purchase Review Form (see PPF attached), to help us vet the opportunity and respond back with a Commercial Quote that you can use in your proposal. With approximately 8-10 week lead times on many of our commercial products, it is important that we receive a PPF at least 90 days prior to the requested delivery date and a PO no later than 75 days. Your cooperation in sending the PPF for review and submitting the PO, once the Commercial Quote becomes acceptable, will be crucial in ensuring a successful and timely delivery.
Please note that if a preliminary or final PPF for this commercial opportunity in not received within 30 days from the date it was created, the project stage will be automatically move from “Qualified“ to “Future Follow-Up”, but will still be reflected in your Commercial Pipeline.
Note: If you are interested in financing options, please complete our Commercial Request for Financing Quotation (see RFQ attached), and email to RFQ@sunpowercorp.com.
I look forward to working with you.
Opportunity {!Opportunity.Link}
